name="additionalParameters" type="AdditionalParametersType"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>Used to send additional Information specific to an accommodationcode For eg: 84 needs multiplier code name=extendedmultiplier,integer=1</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:complexType name="ProfileType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element <xsd:enumeration value="F"/> <xsd:enumeration value="U"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> <xsd:element name="lastName"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The candidate's last or value="collapse"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> <xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="firstName"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The candidate's first name; for example, George.</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> <xsd:simpleType> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:minLength value="2"/> <xsd:maxLength value="30"/> <xsd:whiteSpace value="collapse"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> <xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="middleName"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The candidate's middle name; for example, </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> <xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="prefix" type="xsd:unsignedInt"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>Candidate prefix should be one of these integer suffix should be one of these integer values 1-Jr,2-Sr,3-II,4-III,5-IV</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element> <xsd:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0" name="address" <xsd:documentation>A flag indicating how the candidate prefers to be contacted by ETS. 1-Email, 2-Standard Mail Default is set to 2</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> <xsd:simpleType> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:positiveInteger"> <xsd:maxInclusive value="10"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> <xsd:element default="false" name="validForMarketing" </xsd:element> <xsd:element name="nativeLanguage" type="xsd:string"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The first language the candidate spoke.</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element> <xsd:element name="nativeCountry" type="ISOCountryCodeType"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The country in which the candidate was born.</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element> <xsd:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0" name="accommodations" type="AccommodationType"/> <xsd:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0" name="hobson" </xsd:annotation> </xsd:element> <xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="searchServiceOptInStatus"> <xsd:annotation> <xsd:documentation>The candidate's Search Service Opt IN Status</xsd:documentation> </xsd:annotation> <xsd:simpleType> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="N"/> <xsd:enumeration value="Y"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:element> </xsd:sequence>
